duration: use int64_t for measuring milliseconds

Fixes #45
ci: add doctest-dev
test: use system doctest
test: make unit tests optional
bump version to 0.7.0
add forgotten option and section-impl.hpp
compound-option: ignore values not from config file when building dynamic list
file: do not store compound options
compound-option: don't load values which are valid XML
file: consider lock and which options are present in the config file on reload
make option and section cloning preserve XML mapping

option-base: add basic locking mechanism

This will be useful for plugins which want to lock an option, i.e make
it so that the value of this option is not affected by changes in the
config file.
